
The OLED monitor uses #include "SSD1306Brzo.h" and other great techniques from Squix' library.
This monitor is always powered up.  The button is a link RST > Gnd and so wakes up the ESP whenevr it is needed.
Three loops to display the voltage found on the sender's webpage and then goes to ESP.deepsleep

There's enough space inside the little box for a USB battery charger module and the 16850 battery.  
Cut a hole in the bottom of the box to access the usb socket.
